747-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of Orsi 1893</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Petronios Dionysis, having lived well for 80 years, six months, 15 days, died 7 days before the Ides of July and lies here</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Orsi 1893 305 no. 104 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001715\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001715</a>  </li><li> Strazzulla 1897 152 no. 221 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001390\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001390</a>  </li><li> Wessel 1989 178 no. 753 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
